<br>
I'd say the main thing you need is a haste item. Either Silver Chitin Handwraps, for 2.5-3k, or flowing black silk sash, 1.5-2k. Either way, you'll take a big hit in ac/hp, but either of those haste items will bring the delay of your polearm down to 28, which makes a huge difference.<br>
